{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"06edf59c95","title":"抚钟太夫人联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e42c392e8","index":0,"year":1944,"month":4,"day":10,"articleId":"06edf59c95"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9c07616f29","type":"paragraph","text":"抚钟太夫人联（1944年4月10日）八路功勋，大孝为国一生劳动，吾党光荣。为母当学民族美雄贤母：","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"06edf59c95"},{"id":"a2a48b2c3c","type":"paragraph","text":"斯人无愧劳动阶级究人[1]1944年2月15日，未德的等亲针太夫人遗世，享年86岁。在延安纪念“三八”节的大会上，慈畅宣布了这一消息，号召妇女学习钟太夫人劳动终身和勤检持家的精神。1944年4月10日，延安各界1000多人在杨家岭中央大礼堂举行了连停大会，毛泽东、周恩来、刘少奇等中央领导人参加了追停大会。本文一为毛泽东代表中央题写的找联：本文二是毛泽东以个人名","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"06edf59c95"}],"page":{"id":"d430893442","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"06edf59c95","start":373,"end":373}}}},"__N_SSG":true}